section.simpara:
This module is present even in the base
 &linkset; by default.  When this module is present, &features-var;
 contains the symbol :SYSCALLS.

listitem.simpara:
This is an interface to the &symlink;
    (when &method-r; is :SYMLINK),
    &link; (when it is :HARDLINK), and &rename;
    (when it is :RENAME) system calls, as well as,
    you guessed it, a generic file copy utility (when &method-r; is &copy-k;).
